需要使用到的包

library(fGarch)
library(ggplot2)
library(forecast)
library(tseries)
library(scales)
library(plyr)
library(TTR)
set.seed(2020)

数据特征

daily_2008 <- read.csv("../Data/SP500/08年每日.csv")
SPY <- ts(daily_2008$收盘, frequency = 251, start = c(2008, 1))
Diffrence_of_SPY <- ts(diff(SPY), 
                       frequency = 251, start = c(2008, 1))
par(mfrow=c(1,1))
plot(SPY)

plot(Diffrence_of_SPY)

建模分析

ARIMA模型

定阶

cprice <- diff(daily_2008$收盘)
acf(cprice)

pacf(cprice)

ARIMA1

模型

m2 <- arima(cprice, order = c(3, 0, 0), 
            seasonal = list(order = c(2, 0, 0), period = 5), 
            include.mean = F)
m2
## 
## Call:
## arima(x = cprice, order = c(3, 0, 0), seasonal = list(order = c(2, 0, 0), period = 5), 
##     include.mean = F)
## 
## Coefficients:
##           ar1      ar2     ar3     sar1    sar2
##       -0.1151  -0.0337  0.0943  -0.0708  0.0625
## s.e.   0.0180   0.0186  0.0182   0.0186  0.0192
## 
## sigma^2 estimated as 4.69:  log likelihood = -6752.41,  aic = 13516.81

图像

plot(m2)

checkresiduals(m2)

## 
##  Ljung-Box test
## 
## data:  Residuals from ARIMA(3,0,0)(2,0,0)[5] with zero mean
## Q* = 7.5057, df = 5, p-value = 0.1857
## 
## Model df: 5.   Total lags used: 10

预测

plot(forecast(m2,h=10),xlim=c(3000,3090))

模型

ARMA+GARCH模型

定阶

adjcp <- cprice[11:3081] + 0.0817 * cprice[6:3076] - 0.0667 * cprice[1:3071]
acf(adjcp)

pacf(adjcp)

指数模型

monthly_2008 <- read.csv("../Data/SP500/08年每月.csv")
Monthly_Price<-monthly_2008$收盘
Monthly_Pricets<-ts(Monthly_Price,frequency = 12,start=c(2008,1))
fit_ets<-ets(Monthly_Pricets)
fit_ets
## ETS(M,N,N) 
## 
## Call:
##  ets(y = Monthly_Pricets) 
## 
##   Smoothing parameters:
##     alpha = 0.9999 
## 
##   Initial states:
##     l = 137.0724 
## 
##   sigma:  0.046
## 
##      AIC     AICc      BIC 
## 1345.616 1345.784 1354.587

图像

plot(fit_ets)

预测

plot(forecast(fit_ets),xlab="Time",flty=2)

accuracy(fit_ets)
##                     ME     RMSE      MAE       MPE     MAPE      MASE      ACF1
## Training set 0.7217255 8.607849 5.926743 0.2795169 3.445388 0.2628449 0.0787231
